    <statement>
      <p>Using CSS and HTML Make a webpage that has two columns.  Each column should use half of the width of the page.  The left half should have a light gray background and the right half should have a light green background.  The left half should have a list of the 5 best selling  books in Amazon's kindle store, and the right should have a list of your five favorite celebrities or athletes.</p>
    </statement>
